<div class="clearfix">&nbsp;</div>
<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12">
<div class="outline-testimonial grey"><h2 class="h2-testimonials">"The difference in him is REMARKABLE!"</h2>
<h3>We had my 9 year old son on the GAPS diet for autism for 4 months, we had noticed some mild improvements with diet alone, and then in the fourth month we found VSL#3, which was recommended by Dr. Bryce Wylde. He has now been through 3 boxes, he takes it twice a day. The difference in him is REMARKABLE! Probiotics and diet are changing my son's life. It's a financial burden but worth every penny in the end. I highly recommend this product and omitting irritating foods. </h3>
