<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12">
<div class="outline-testimonial grey"><h2 class="h2-testimonials">"I was diagnosed in June 2003 with severe ulcerative colitis."</h2>
<h3>I tried all the treatments available and imaginable (Pentasa, Imuran, Remicade, Humira, and different types of steroids) without any noticeable improvement except for high dosage of the steroids but the use long term will damage the body.<br>
<br>
I also tried all sorts of natural/holistic treatments including  probiotics, hypnotherapy, acupuncture, shiatsu treatments without any relief.<br>
<br>
Then I saw a Father's testimony of his son's experience: after an operation the boy took VSL#3 and his condition improved considerably, I wanted to try
it.<br>
<br>
I have been taking VSL#3 for the past 3 months (1 sachet at the end of my supper). Within one week of taking VSL#3, I was sleeping through the night,
